Usage:

This is CSSParser which follows 2.1 CSS specification.

Usage:

CSSFactory.parse() to parse either file or string
to generate StyleSheet 

CSSFactory.assign() together with Document DOM, StyleSheet,
and selected media type to create mapping between elements
and their CSS declarations.

Use ANT build file to generate jar. Libraries can be fetched from
SVN. 

Required libraries are:

logging:
slf4j as facade and an arbitrary implementation


html parsing:
Tidy-8.0.jar

parser core:
antlr-runtime 3.1

optional testing:
junit-4.4.jar
